The process that took place from 1975 to 1991 between Morocco, Algeria and Mauritania is giving a solid shape to this question, which is becoming one of the most important issues of the 21st century, and still unreachable for the peoples under dispute. Accordingly, the factor of civilization with long heritage of the region and the factors coming together socio-politically is only available in the analysis based on humanitarian approaches. Based on the goal of being founded on human rights, the former mixed mission of UNAET and the present mission of MONUSCO can assuredly be defined as « an instrument of humanitarian perspective.” The missions juxtaposed with peacekeeping mission of MINURSO allow the people a chance to live in peace in peacekeepers to investigate fearlessly, but considering the conditions that allow peacekeeping operations to change gradually to political problems the impact that UNRI and the borthers of peacekeeping forces have on a possible solution to the past and future is also found under scrutiny.

Keywords: Marx, Durkheim, Simmel, Albert, Development
